Happy 228th Birthday, America!
 On July 4th, 1776, we claimed our independence from Great Britain (now United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland) and Democracy was born. Every day thousands leave their homeland to come to the &ldquo;land of the free and the home of the brave&rdquo; so they can begin their American Dream.
